Day 5 â€“ HTML Links and Images

Links connect webpages using <a> tag.
The href attribute specifies the URL.
Images are inserted using <img src="path" alt="description">.
Example:

<a href="https://example.com">Visit Site</a>
<img src="photo.jpg" alt="My Photo" width="200">


You can also link email using mailto: and open links in new tabs using target="_blank".
